data.description: Discover versatile living in this 3,349 sq. ft. single-family home with 9 bedrooms and 5 bathrooms—a blend of functionality and flexibility. The main unit offers 3 beds/2 baths, with the 2nd unit providing 3 beds/1 bath + an outdoor shower. The 3rd unit features 1 bed/1 bath + a kitchenette, while the 4th unit includes 2 beds + a toilet. Ideal for family or investment, this well-maintained, multi-unit gem is conveniently located near town, boasting mountain views and a cool climate.  This property accommodates various living arrangements, whether it's an investment opportunity or a spacious home for extended family. Positioned near town, it offers easy access to amenities and picturesque mountain views that enhance the natural beauty of the surroundings. Furthermore, this home is exceptionally well-maintained, ready for you to move in and make it your own. The multiple units on the property offer endless potential for income generation, housing extended family members, or creating separate living spaces to cater to various needs.
